PKI

Todays reading was on the topic of PKI public key infrastructure, there are a lot of factors related to pki but
but an are of pki is the managing of keys and certificates that are assioated with keys this is defined my the process of
authenticating a device with a user digitally. this authentication process creates a trusted relationship between the user
and the devicethis process includes a digital creation of a key and and a CA certificate that validates both the user and
the device and allows the user to enteract witht he device.
